    "created_at": "2016-04-13T02:18:42Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-13T02:19:38Z",
    "body": "You are correct. Unless you `printToPDF()` you cannot set margins for `print()` as options. Being that the CSS method is the current specification and Chrome nor any other browser vendor has plans to extend on `print()` beyond event handlers per [the latest specifications](https://w3c.github.io/html/webappapis.html#printing) I am unsure if this will be implemented in Electron anytime soon.\n"
  },
